OL,3,CDetectives granted additional time to
OL,4,Cquestion man over Portadown murder
OL,6,FDetectives investigating a murder in
OL,7,FPortadown have been given more time to
OL,8,Fquestion a man.
OL,10,FPolice received a report of an
OL,11,Faltercation at a property in the
OL,12,FRanfurley Road area shortly after 11pm
OL,13,Fon Thursday.
OL,15,FRolandas Kvederis, 49, was pronounced
OL,16,Fdead at the scene.
OL,18,FTwo men had been arrested on suspicion
OL,19,Fof murder.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
