OL,3,CDetectives granted additional time to
OL,4,Cquestion man over Portadown murder
OL,6,FThe PSNI said detectives have now been
OL,7,Fgranted additional time by a court to
OL,8,Fquestion a man aged in his 50s.
OL,10,FA second man, aged in his 50s, has
OL,11,Fbeen released unconditionally.
